headline.main: 97-Year-Old Twins Who Died Together Remembered as Inspiring
headline.print_headline: 97-Year-Old Twins Who Died Together Remembered as Inspiring

lead_paragraph: The family of 97-year-old twin sisters who died in freezing temperatures after falling outside one of their homes says the two lived with charm, grace, kindness and style.
